content: Here's a rough list of my expenses. I remember buying gifts for my sister's birthday, my friend's baby shower, and my neighbor who just moved in. I also got some stuff for my grandma's visit, and some essentials for my roommate when she was sick. And then there was the office potluck lunch where I got snacks and drinks for my coworkers - I spent around $50 on chips and dips from Costco, and soda and water from the convenience store near my apartment.
